      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A fluent, type-safe builder for constructing <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronExpression\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instances.</p>\n<p>\nProvides both raw field methods (<xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder.WithMinutes(System.String)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>) and\nhigh-level convenience methods (<xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder.EveryNMinutes(System.Int32)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\n<xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder.AtTime(System.Int32%2cSystem.Int32)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder.OnDaysOfWeek(System.DayOfWeek%5b%5d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>).\n</p>\n<example>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">var expr = new CronBuilder()\n    .AtTime(9, 0)\n    .OnDaysOfWeek(DayOfWeek.Monday, DayOfWeek.Wednesday, DayOfWeek.Friday)\n    .Build();\n// produces \"0 9 * * 1,3,5\"</code></pre>\n</example>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronExpression.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronExpression.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Ampere.Str.Cron.CronExpression",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronExpression.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An immutable, thread-safe representation of a fully parsed cron expression.</p>\n<p>\nSupports standard 5-field (minute–DOW), 6-field with seconds, and 7-field\nwith seconds + year formats.  Also supports Quartz-style extensions: <code>L</code>,\n<code>W</code>, <code>LW</code>, <code>#</code>, and <code>?</code>.\n</p>\n<p>\nUse <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronParser.Parse(System.String)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to obtain instances, or <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronBuilder\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nto construct them fluently.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronField.yml",
