        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronField.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Ampere.Str.Cron.CronField",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronField.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents a single parsed field (e.g. minutes, hours) of a cron expression.\nA field contains one or more <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronNode\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> elements (the comma-separated parts).\nInstances are immutable and thread-safe.</p>\n"
    },
