      "Title": "Ampere.Str.Cron.CronStepNode",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Ampere.Str.Cron.CronStepNode.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A step expression (e.g. <code>* /5</code>, <code>1-10/2</code>, <code>0/15</code>).\nThe <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronStepNode.Base\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is the range or wildcard; the <xref href=\"Ampere.Str.Cron.CronStepNode.Step\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is the increment.</p>\n"
